{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 762015, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可以的，cz觉得自学完全够了", "timestamp": 1608735494, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762019, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "三天实习，两天看看ppt，休息两天", "timestamp": 1608735513, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762021, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一周实习四天，看ppt一天，休息两天", "timestamp": 1608735530, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762023, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大几啊课那么多？", "timestamp": 1608735538, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762051, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "对于经管想去业界工作的同学来说，翘课实习不是基本操作吗", "timestamp": 1608735843, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762052, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可是cz不听课只看ppt真的没法handle啊\n天赋注定呜呜呜", "timestamp": 1608735843, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762054, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "看大几了", "timestamp": 1608735861, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762063, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 大二呢", "timestamp": 1608736011, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762075, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 说句实话看目标 如果人均bb人上人那就跟着自己规划走 读研的话又不急", "timestamp": 1608736163, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762458, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz大二，感谢楼上各位！", "timestamp": 1608738824, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762520, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "大二【非常】不建议学期中实习，当时我们辅导员甚至明令禁止。这种要求时间长、到岗天数多的实习，大多是为大三及以上的同学准备的，要学期中实习也建议大三再开始", "timestamp": 1608739198, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762543, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz现在就在招实习生，信我，大二的我一律不考虑。即使是我自己上到研二了，都还是觉得同时handle两天的课+三天的实习很痛苦", "timestamp": 1608739292, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 763231, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 啊，谢谢Grace，但是前期一点实习经验都没有，那大二小学期实习会不会很难找啊", "timestamp": 1608767538, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 764206, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 当然，cz身边也有大二就学期中实习的同学，只是总体上来说，我觉得不是很建议~第一份实习确实会难找一些，可以多利用一下学院提供的资源，比如多参加一些校友活动，请校友帮忙看有无机会（cz的第一份暑期实习就是这么找的），也可以关注一些求职类的公众号，进他们的群看发布的实习内容，也可以先从门槛较低的PTA之类的做起，dz加油！大家最后都会找到的所以别太着急", "timestamp": 1608783951, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 764440, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 好的，谢谢Grace！因为dz其实是有点社恐的，虽然在经管有点不合时宜，所以还是更偏向海投，内推真的好难啊，social也好难，唉", "timestamp": 1608787293, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 764989, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 158634, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 哈哈我也超级社恐，不要害怕，一般来愿意参与学院活动的校友都是超级nice的，一些学长学姐也会很愿意帮忙，有时候迈出那一步去试一试会有意想不到的结果。海投也是一种方法，当然会辛苦一些，总之加油！", "timestamp": 1608794552, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 11, "pid": 158634, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "求问大家都会翘课实习吗，dz看一般要求都是3个月以上，至少三天。坐标经管", "timestamp": 1608735438, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1608794554, "url": "", "vote": {}}}